  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARE YOU READY FOR ADVENTURE</h2>As an outlaw alchemist drifting around the ocean. While exploring an abandoned pirate ship, You have uncovered rats who have been corrupted by the evil spirits of the deep. It is your duty to pick up magical slingshot paired with alchemical projectiles to exterminate these monsters and uncover the secret in the ship.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485150/extras/525e76114c22eafdb1502071aa3ae2f9.poster.avif?t=1704333952\" width=580 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485150/extras/525e76114c22eafdb1502071aa3ae2f9.webm?t=1704333952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485150/extras/525e76114c22eafdb1502071aa3ae2f9.mp4?t=1704333952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>WIELD YOUR SLINGSHOT</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic VR aiming and shooting mechanism with the magical Slingshot. <br></li><li>Don't hesitate to shoot the devil creature.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485150/extras/c2cf1aa5839fcee9f308ad68a5c150d4.poster.avif?t=1704333952\" width=580 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485150/extras/c2cf1aa5839fcee9f308ad68a5c150d4.webm?t=1704333952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485150/extras/c2cf1aa5839fcee9f308ad68a5c150d4.mp4?t=1704333952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>SPECIAL PROJACTILE</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use different types of projectiles to develop your own style of strategy and grow as you play.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485150/extras/1a7643a81f5bee23c5bcd1e4e666cbaa.poster.avif?t=1704333952\" width=580 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485150/extras/1a7643a81f5bee23c5bcd1e4e666cbaa.webm?t=1704333952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2485150/extras/1a7643a81f5bee23c5bcd1e4e666cbaa.mp4?t=1704333952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>RICH CONTENT AND UNIQUE CREATURE</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meticulously crafted level designs and engaging interactive elements.<br></li><li>Advanced AI and mysterious evil boss. Learn to exploit their weaknesses.</li></ul>",
